Class UsersModel

java.lang.Object
ticktocktrack.logic.UsersModel
public class UsersModel extends Object
Represents a user in the system, which can be an Admin, Teacher, or Student. Holds user-related information including identifiers, personal details, role, and metadata such as who created the user and when.
